Source.Name: falkon
Source.Summary: Falkon (formerly QupZilla) is a new and very fast QtWebEngine browser
Source.Description: Falkon is a KDE web browser using QtWebEngine rendering engine, previously known as QupZilla. It aims to be a lightweight web browser available through all major platforms. This project has been originally started only for educational purposes. But from its start, Falkon has grown into a feature-rich browser.
